      • getPendingClosingChannelsList

        @Deprecated
public java.util.List<LightningApi.PendingChannelsResponse.ClosedChannel> getPendingClosingChannelsList()
        Deprecated.
        Deprecated: Channels pending closing previously contained cooperatively
